Sweet / no triple sec:

    lime juice : simple syrup : tequila [ : orange juice ]
    1          : 1            : 2       [ : 1            ]


Classic / no simple syrup / for less sweet more balanced:

    tequila : triple sec : lime [ : frozen mango ]
    50      : 20         : 15   [ : 20 ]

    Add 2 tsp sug over ice before shaking
